  <text x="210" y="38" font-family="Georgia,serif" font-size="10" fill="#444">∫ₐᵇ f(x)dx = lim(n→∞) Σ f(xᵢ)·Δx   |   shown: y=x², from 0 to 2, n=4 rectangles</text>

  <!-- Axes -->
  <line x1="60" y1="340" x2="480" y2="340" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2.5"/>
